http://localhost:8081/...

authentication/login (POST)
    Message required with username en password as key-value pair in the body
    x-www-form-urlencoded
    returns access_token and refresh_token in body
    structure tokens: see Word document
authentication/token/refresh (GET)
    In the header: Bearer+space+<refresh token>
    (Always this format for all requests)
    (See screenshots from Postman in messenger)

